
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
# Python scripts for modeling polarization and Faraday rotation for a galaxy,	    #
# with external observer.							    # 
#										    #
# by Shannon Vanderwoude							    #
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------##


model_rotate ... Changes LOS of the observer.
model_galaxy ... Outputs .dat file with Stokes I, Q, U and errors to make Faraday spectra.
		 Built for use with C. Purcell's RMtools package.
